The paper deals with multimodal machine translation, which involves both natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV) techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which covers NLP and related areas. The second most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), which covers CV and related areas. The paper also involves machine learning (ML) techniques, which are covered by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper deals with multimodal data, which is covered by cs.MM (Multimedia).
